_localstatus=0
specialMount() {
  local device="$1"
  local mountPoint="$2"
  local options="$3"
  local fsType="$4"

  if mountpoint -q "$mountPoint"; then
    local options="remount,$options"
  else
    mkdir -p "$mountPoint"
    chmod 0755 "$mountPoint"
  fi
  mount -t "$fsType" -o "$options" "$device" "$mountPoint"
}
